This folder contains test and example scripts and programs.

test_CTA.cpp               - CTA classes test program
                             This program will be compiled and executed after typing
                             > make check
                             in the GammaLib source repository. If an older version of
                             GammaLib exists, make sure to install the new version
                             before using
                             > make install

example_sim_photons.py     - Python script to illustrate MC simulation of photons
                             After installing GammaLib, type
                             > ./example_sim_photons.py
                             If matplotlib is installed, the spectrum will be displayed
                             on the screen.
